      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people... but it's not about needing a listener. it's just that the person i was is gone. and the thing that's left, this \"shell\" i mentioned, it doesn't even have a purpose anymore. it's just taking up space. sometimes it feels more like a burden than a person. it's like i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up to the part that already died.",
